name: Travel Trouble Princess
summary:
Operation Description

A Button :
Ask your princess to jump.

Sword in the right hand :
Swinging a sword against a monster to reduce the monster's HP.

Left-hand umbrella :

By covering the princess with the shadow of the umbrella
the princess's health will not be depleted.

Story

Once upon a time,
there was a kind-hearted princess.
She was heartbroken by the world's ongoing war with monsters.

One day, she decides to go to the temple of the God of Creation
at the end of the world to pray for...
